claim.claim-text:
6. A method for diagnosing shift registers, comprising: pairing together shift registers; 
adding scan-path crossovers between the paired shift registers at intervals along the bit length of each shift register; and 
for each pair of shift registers, using the scan-path crossovers to map output signals from one of the pair of shift registers to the other of the pair of shift registers to localize faults in the shift registers.
